    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A Telepredicted creature uses an effect that requires a Reflex save or attempts to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Dt6B1slsBy8ipJu9]{Disarm} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.ge56Lu1xXVFYUnLP]{Trip} you.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong> You have a bonus against the target using Telepredict. </p><hr /><p>By reading cues and analyzing probability outcomes, you smoothly predicting your opponent's next move. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your Reflex save or Reflex DC against the triggering action. Increase this bonus to +2 if you've dealt mental damage to the target since the last time you used Telepredict.</p>",
